en_868430_0	The renowned meditation practitioner, Ven Diyasenpura Wimala Thero, the resident monk at ‘Bavunseth Mind Relaxing Meditation Centre’ at Hellummahara, Dekatana conducted one more meditation session for three lady Officers and forty three Other Ranks of the Sri Lanka Army on Friday (12).
en_868430_1	It was organized at the request of the Directorate of Psychological Operations at the Army Headquarters.
